      "collapse": "hide",
      "content": {
        "columnOne": "## Know Your Rights!\r\n\r\nWe provide legal education and support to our communities to ensure everyone is staying safe under new laws. We support our mission through education by:\r\n\r\n- Hosting workshops with community partners on how cannabis impacts your legal rights, including housing, employment, and immigration status. Check them out in our partners section!\r\n- Sharing resources and events on expungement, and promoting awareness of new legal vulnerabilities or protections afforded for the use of cannabis.\r\n- Creating educational resources like our crutch cards, designed to inform the public of continued prohibited situations for the possession and consumption of cannabis.\r\n- Providing online resources and videos\r\n",
        "columnTwo": "# Squirrel Ipsum\r\n\r\n\r\n[Squiritur](https://www.thesquirrelcensus.com/) sunt **optima**. Et ascendentes arbores et saltare amant ex genere est. Et si pascere *nuces* sunt valde dolor et facti sunt amici tui.",
